          "prompt_html": "<h1>TABLE COMPLETION 12</h1><p><strong>Questions 21 - 26</strong></p><p>Complete the tables.</p><p>Use <strong>NO MORE THAN TWO WORDS AND / OR A NUMBER</strong> for each answer.</p><p>World’s most spoken languages (by number of individual speakers)</p><table class=\"table-first-col-center\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Rank</strong></th><th><strong>Language</strong></th><th><strong>Number of speakers</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>Mandarin Chinese</td><td>836 million</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>Hindi</td><td>333 million</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td><blank data-qid=\"q21\"/></td><td>332 million</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>English</td><td>Unclear - over <blank data-qid=\"q22\"/> million</td></tr></tbody></table><p>World’s most spoken languages (by number of user countries)</p><table class=\"table-first-col-center\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Rank</strong></th><th><strong>Language</strong></th><th><strong>Number of countries</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>English</td><td>115</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>French</td><td>35</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td><blank data-qid=\"q23\"/></td><td>24</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>Spanish</td><td><blank data-qid=\"q24\"/></td></tr></tbody></table><p>World’s most influential languages (six weighing factors)</p><table class=\"table-first-col-center\"><thead><tr><th>1</th><th>Number of primary speakers</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>2</td><td>Number of secondary speakers</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>Number and <blank data-qid=\"q25\"/> of countries where languages are used</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>Number of major fields using the language internationally</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td><blank data-qid=\"q26\"/> of countries using the language</td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>Socio-literary prestige of the language</td></tr></tbody></table>",
